data.title: C Site + Waterfall Teleport from C Main
data.description: Here is a potentially high risk C Main Rendezvous Setup that allows you to hold off angles inside of C Site, or push into Waterfall. Use this to expand your options, but don't force a play into Waterfall without enough information.
